            <div class="technical-section__item">
                <div class="technical-section__icon">🔗</div>
                <h3 class="technical-section__item-title">Integrirana Zaštita</h3>
                <p class="technical-section__item-desc">Kristali postaju dio betonske strukture — ne ljušte se, ne pucaju i ne zahtijevaju zamjenu.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="technical-section__item">
                <div class="technical-section__icon">🔄</div>
                <h3 class="technical-section__item-title">Samozarastanje</h3>
                <p class="technical-section__item-desc">Pri kontaktu s novom vodom dormantni kristali se reakiviraju i zatvaraju pukotine do 0.5 mm.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="technical-section__item">
                <div class="technical-section__icon">⏳</div>
                <h3 class="technical-section__item-title">Doživotni Vijek</h3>
                <p class="technical-section__item-desc">Za razliku od membrana koje imaju ograničen vijek trajanja, XYPEX traje koliko i sam beton.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="technical-section__item">
                <div class="technical-section__icon">↩️</div>
